      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, refreshing themselves with the provisions set before them. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Behold, certain sons of Belial — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Children of the devil, wicked and licentious men. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Bring forth the man, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — They wanted the Levite brought forth, that they might satisfy their unnatural lusts. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "This man is come into my house ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— And therefore I am obliged to protect him by the laws of hospitality. As several circumstances of this horrid wickedness resemble those of the affair recorded Genesis 19., we refer the reader to the notes on that chapter.",
        "children": []
      },
